{
  "stem": "2118.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But the group he came, they were sent away, and I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And this was already in September '44.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "From there, we were sent away into a-- a working camp, to Sonneberg-- Sonneberg and [INAUDIBLE], which is very close to Weimar, the city of Weimar.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And it was this big factory, GE Reinhardt, if I remember going back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] they were making gears-- gears for tanks or airplanes or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I came in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They took us down and they set us up and then made a big line.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And that chef came down, a chef that-- the chef, he would call them here there director or whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he made a big speech.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It's all your fault.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "The Juden wanted the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The Juden are to blame and now you've going to work and you're going to this and that-- blew a lot of-- this were supposed to be the pep talk-- blew a lot of air.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "OK, we didn't pay much attention to him anyway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Then they come out and ask somebody who has any kind of mechanical experience.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So I said I do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went out and asked me what can you work on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, I can work in a drill press, a punch press.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they put me on a machine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a long machine, maybe 10 meter long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it had this giant roll in the middle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you put down this big wheel which weighed about at least 50 pounds.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You secured it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You put the pin through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very hard work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Secured it from the other side and you had a handle, and you turned on the machine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the machine pulled that giant roll through the hole of that gear.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
